title: Black golfer excited to make PGA Tour debut at Frys.com Open
text:
Photo: Sam Greenwood, Getty Images Harold Varner III will make his debut on the PGA Tour this week in Napa. Harold Varner III will make his debut on the PGA Tour this week in...
Many times on the Web.com Tour this past season, Harold Varner III glanced into the gallery and noticed an African American kid traipsing along, following him.
